On the three black minivans directed to the monastery built around the cave where the Christian monk lived as an hermit, travel about thirty Europeans of the Ecr. A wide range of European Conservatives of different nationalities: Italian, Spanish, Finnish, Cypriot, and French. They come from Brussels where today Giorgia Meloni> has claimed, after the European Council, the results obtained from Italy. And the mission overlaps the day still 'hot' with the opposition to the Premier attack after the words on Ventotene.
